	* BUGFIX: a better one for parse error when input full parts of IP.
	* IMPROVEMENT: default value area is more pretty.
	* IMPROVEMENT: multi-arguments support of error prompt.
	* IMPROVEMENT: replace all 'echo;...' with 'echo ...'.

